    <div n="1"><head><hi rendition="#i">Extent and Population of America.</hi></head><p>&#x2014;The fol-<lb/>lowing estimate of the extent, in square leagues<lb/>and population, of the
                    Continent of America in<lb/>1822, was lately transmitted by Baron de
                    Hum-<lb/>holdt from Paris, to President Bolivar, with the<lb/>accompanying
                    letter:</p> <lb break="yes"/>
                    <lb break="yes"/>
                <table>
                    <row>
                        <cell/>
                        <cell> Square Leagues.</cell>
                        <cell> Population.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <lb break="yes"/>
                    <row>
                        <cell>Mexico, or New Spain</cell>
                        <cell>75,830</cell>
                        <cell>6,800,000</cell>
                    </row>
                    <lb break="yes"/>
                    <row>
                        <cell>Guatemala</cell>
                        <cell>16,740</cell>
                        <cell>1,600,000</cell>
                    </row>
                    <lb break="yes"/>
                    <row>
                        <cell>Cuba and Puerto Rico</cell>
                        <cell>4,430</cell>
                        <cell>800,000</cell>
                    </row>
                    <lb break="yes"/>
                    <row>
                        <cell rows="3">Colombia <list rendition="#leftBraced">
                                <item>Venezuela</item>
                                <item>New Granada</item>
                            </list></cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell>33,700</cell>
                        <cell>900,000</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell>58,250</cell>
                        <cell>1,800,000</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row/>
                    <row>
                        <cell>Peru</cell>
                        <cell>42,150</cell>
                        <cell>1,400,000</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell>Chili</cell>
                        <cell>14,240</cell>
                        <cell>1,100,000</cell>
                    </row>
                    <lb break="yes"/>
                    <row>
                        <cell>Buenos Ayres</cell>
                        <cell>126,770</cell>
                        <cell>2,000,000</cell>
                    </row>
                    <lb break="yes"/>
                    <row>
                        <cell/>
                        <cell>_____________</cell>
                        <cell>_____________</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell>Total formerly Spanish</cell>
                        <cell>372,110</cell>
                        <cell>16,400,000</cell>
                    </row>
                    <lb break="yes"/>
                    <row>
                        <cell>   United States</cell>
